{"tid":1775750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「破產指引」經濟唔好要攬炒","createTime":"2019-12-09T04:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T05:02:51.000Z","uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b0751ca918851bfd85332cf01ab1a7354a5e2b","tid":1775750,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要嘅係</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">搵人搞係2萬內<br />\n過兩萬蚊唔好理佢<br />\n自己搞1萬蚊左右<br />\n詳見<a href=\"http://hkiva.org/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=2005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkiva.org%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D2005&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=e78c228d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkiva.org/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=2005</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n入紙申請破產到正式破產需時最少1個月<br />\n(文件有錯會瘋狂俾法官押後審）<br />\n期間收數佬會瘋狂搵你<br />\n唔洗理佢，屋企門口裝閉路電視<br />\n佢上門你拖佢入屋斬鳩佢都無事（我諗）<br />\n你有破產保護同埋佢非法入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">破產呈請個時寫生活費好重要</span>（假設18000)<br />\n到出左人工（22000)<br />\n你每個月要去匯豐銀行排隊入4000蚊<br />\n所以你去開戶口最好揀返匯豐黎開<br />\n(破左所有戶口無晒要再過，只能開一個）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">正常</span>一個人18000蚊生活費係絕對無問題<br />\n再大啲我就唔知啦<br />\n而被人即時解僱個通知金係要上繳<br />\n但因為失業你可以申請只係交4000蚊個個數<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">最後無欠多過廿萬都唔好諗破產呢條路</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c9f52683ced44ba4b5a99fa1aecbd98d4e0a35","tid":1775750,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"對唔住🙇🏻&zwj;♂️，借個位宣傳一下：<br />\n<br />\n和你開工會：七人成團，重光勞工界，只剩唔夠四個月！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775618</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8caa842f012f8db8bc77573a10dd833ea0a54d6c","tid":1775750,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"以我所知好多人假破產<br />\n借完一大畢錢 min pay 還三個月再老破<br />\n亦有聽人講過借錢去做手術變性再老破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次個破產的士佬撞人<br />\n話唔見左十萬rolex 就知幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要收52萬"}]}